{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-challenges-fill-in-the-blank-show-tsx","path":"/learn/b1-english-for-developers/learn-how-to-express-decisions-based-on-comparisons/task-2","result":{"data":{"challengeNode":{"challenge":{"title":"Vežba 2","description":"","instructions":"<section id=\"instructions\">\n<p>Poslušaj zvuk i dovrši rečenicu ispod.</p>\n</section>","explanation":"<section id=\"explanation\">\n<p><span class=\"highlighted-text\">Better</span> je vrsta komparativnog prideva za <span class=\"highlighted-text\">good</span> koji se koristi prilikom poređenja dve stvari.</p>\n<p>U poređenju, pridevi ili glagoli sa jednim slogom obično se dodaju <span class=\"highlighted-text\">-er</span> (kao <span class=\"highlighted-text\">stronger</span> i <span class=\"highlighted-text\">faster</span>) na kraju.</p>\n<p>Pridjevima ili dugim glagolima se koriste <span class=\"highlighted-text\">more</span> (kao <span class=\"highlighted-text\">more interesting</span> i <span class=\"highlighted-text\">more efficiently</span>). <span class=\"highlighted-text\">More</span> je komparativna reč koja se koristi za pokazivanje veće količine, nivoa ili broja nečega u poređenju sa nečim drugim.</p>\n<p>Neki drugi reči imaju neobičan tip poređenja, kao što <span class=\"highlighted-text\">good</span> se menja u <span class=\"highlighted-text\">better</span>. Primer:</p>\n<p><span class=\"highlighted-text\">Cloud storage is better than local storage for remote access.</span> – To znači da cloud baza podataka podržava udaljeni pristup, dok lokalna baza podataka nema ili nije dobra u toj mogućnosti.</p>\n</section>","challengeType":22,"helpCategory":"English","superBlock":"b1-english-for-developers","block":"learn-how-to-express-decisions-based-on-comparisons","lang":"en-US","fields":{"slug":"/learn/b1-english-for-developers/learn-how-to-express-decisions-based-on-comparisons/task-2"},"fillInTheBlank":{"sentence":"<p>Can you help me decide which one is BLANK for security?</p>","blanks":[{"answer":"better","feedback":"<p>Ovo reči je vrsta komparativnog prideva za <span class=\"highlighted-text\">good</span> i koristi se prilikom poređenja dve opcije. Ukazuje da je jedna bolja po kvalitetu ili performansi.</p>"}]},"inputType":null,"tests":[],"transcript":null,"scene":{"setup":{"background":"company2-center.png","characters":[{"character":"Sophie","position":{"x":50,"y":0,"z":1.4},"opacity":0}],"audio":{"filename":"B1_13-1.mp3","startTime":1,"startTimestamp":4,"finishTimestamp":6.12},"alwaysShowDialogue":null},"commands":[{"background":null,"character":"Sophie","position":null,"opacity":1,"startTime":0,"finishTime":null,"dialogue":null},{"background":null,"character":"Sophie","position":null,"opacity":null,"startTime":1,"finishTime":3.12,"dialogue":{"text":"Can you help me decide which one is better for security?","align":"center"}},{"background":null,"character":"Sophie","position":null,"opacity":0,"startTime":3.62,"finishTime":null,"dialogue":null}]},"translationPending":false}}},"pageContext":{"challengeMeta":{"blockHashSlug":"/learn/b1-english-for-developers/#learn-how-to-express-decisions-based-on-comparisons","dashedName":"task-2","certification":"b1-english-for-developers","disableLoopProtectTests":false,"disableLoopProtectPreview":false,"superBlock":"b1-english-for-developers","chapter":null,"module":null,"block":"learn-how-to-express-decisions-based-on-comparisons","isFirstStep":false,"template":null,"required":[],"isLastChallengeInBlock":false,"nextChallengePath":"/learn/b1-english-for-developers/learn-how-to-express-decisions-based-on-comparisons/task-3","prevChallengePath":"/learn/b1-english-for-developers/learn-how-to-express-decisions-based-on-comparisons/task-1","id":"67c458aa5ff69775e78e0eef","saveSubmissionToDB":null},"projectPreview":{"challengeData":{"challengeType":19,"challengeFiles":[]}},"id":"/learn/b1-english-for-developers/learn-how-to-express-decisions-based-on-comparisons/task-2"}},"staticQueryHashes":["3858